In this kind of scope we consider everything related to that organisation in that scope which include:
    Any subdomain
    Child Domain
    Any Assets own by that organisation
    
Recon consist of":
              Subsidary & Acquisition Enumeration
              Reverse Lookup
              ASN & IP Space Enumeration
              Subdomain Enumeration
              Subdomain Takeover
              Probing & Technology Fingerprinting
              Port Scanning
              Known vulnerability
              Template Base Scanning
              Misconfigured Cloud / Assets
              Broken Link Hijacking
              Directory Enumeration
              Hardcoded Information in JavaScript
              Github Recon & Google Dorking
              Data breach Analysis
              Parameter Fuzzing
              Search Engine Discovery (Shodan, Censys etc.)
              HeartBleed Scanning
              
